<i>One month.</i>

3
00:01:14,120 --> 00:01:15,880
<i>I'll give you one month.</i>

4
00:01:15,960 --> 00:01:17,640
<i>If you don't come back,</i>

5
00:01:18,440 --> 00:01:19,280
<i>I won't wait anymore.</i>

6
00:01:27,320 --> 00:01:28,480
<i>Li Jinyu…</i>

7
00:01:30,920 --> 00:01:32,640
Don't tell me you can't live without me.

8
00:01:33,400 --> 00:01:34,600
I don't know.

9
00:01:38,720 --> 00:01:40,040
Don't know?

10
00:01:40,960 --> 00:01:42,600
So, is that a yes or a no?

11
00:01:58,920 --> 00:01:59,800
Don't start.

12
00:02:05,640 --> 00:02:06,800
Wait for me to come back.

13
00:02:16,960 --> 00:02:19,800
DESTINATION JIANGBEI

14
00:02:38,640 --> 00:02:39,520
Ye Meng!

15
00:02:41,240 --> 00:02:42,440
Ye Meng!

16
00:02:42,960 --> 00:02:46,000
- Could you be any louder?
- Ms. Ye, the great beauty herself.

17
00:02:46,080 --> 00:02:47,480
Did Gou Kai send you to pick me up?

18
00:02:47,560 --> 00:02:49,080
Him? No way.

19
00:02:49,160 --> 00:02:50,440
With our friendship?

20
00:02:51,160 --> 00:02:53,040
Picking up a beauty is my honor.

21
00:02:56,320 --> 00:02:57,840
Sharper.

22
00:02:57,920 --> 00:02:58,960
More striking.

23
00:02:59,520 --> 00:03:01,160
What, was the weather over there better?

24
00:03:01,240 --> 00:03:02,520
You're glowing even more now.

25
00:03:02,600 --> 00:03:04,760
And you've only gotten greasier.

26
00:03:06,520 --> 00:03:07,520
The car's right there.

27
00:03:09,240 --> 00:03:11,960
Just landed. A friend's picking me up.

28
00:03:12,040 --> 00:03:14,680
Did you get out of bed yet?
Don't skip breakfast.

29
00:03:16,400 --> 00:03:18,400
"Did you get out of bed yet"?

30
00:03:18,480 --> 00:03:19,560
What is wrong with you?

31
00:03:19,640 --> 00:03:21,280
Reporting in to the boyfriend, huh?

32
00:03:22,040 --> 00:03:24,120
Look at you, honeymoon phase and all.
If Gou Kai saw this,

33
00:03:24,200 --> 00:03:25,640
he'd be crushed.

34
00:03:25,720 --> 00:03:27,000
Correction.

35
00:03:27,080 --> 00:03:28,880
It's not the honeymoon "phase".

36
00:03:28,960 --> 00:03:31,200
It's the honeymoon. We're married.

37
00:03:42,480 --> 00:03:43,720
Already ate.

38
00:03:43,800 --> 00:03:45,360
Everyone's doing fine.

39
00:03:46,480 --> 00:03:48,600
MESSAGE TO YE MENG

40
00:03:52,000 --> 00:03:55,000
You only made it official a few days ago,
and I'm supposed to believe it?

41
00:03:56,280 --> 00:03:57,920
So, how'd you two even meet?

42
00:03:58,960 --> 00:04:00,920
Not telling you.

43
00:04:01,800 --> 00:04:03,520
Come on. Spill.

44
00:04:03,600 --> 00:04:04,960
Introduce us.

45
00:04:14,520 --> 00:04:19,519
YE MENG'S MEETING GOU KAI LATER
MAKE SURE YOU'RE THERE

46
00:04:28,520 --> 00:04:29,400
Ping'an,

47
00:04:31,240 --> 00:04:33,080
what's the most important thing
in a marriage?

48
00:04:34,640 --> 00:04:35,480
Tell me.

49
00:04:39,560 --> 00:04:42,320
That's right. Trust.

50
00:05:01,600 --> 00:05:02,560
Ms. Ye Meng.

51
00:05:03,800 --> 00:05:05,080
- You're back, Ms. Ye Meng.
- Hi.

52
00:05:06,440 --> 00:05:07,520
GEOMETRY FIELD

53
00:05:07,600 --> 00:05:08,480
Ms. Ye.

54
00:05:09,960 --> 00:05:11,160
How's everything going?

55
00:05:11,240 --> 00:05:12,400
Same as always.

56
00:05:12,480 --> 00:05:14,360
Ms. Ye, ever since you left,

57
00:05:14,440 --> 00:05:16,040
our workload doubled.

58
00:05:16,120 --> 00:05:17,720
We're exhausted.

59
00:05:18,560 --> 00:05:20,680
Ms. Ye, you're coming back
this time, right?

60
00:05:21,360 --> 00:05:23,440
No, just here to handle some things.

61
00:05:23,520 --> 00:05:24,840
You guys make it sound like

62
00:05:24,920 --> 00:05:26,760
Gou Kai and I treat you so badly.

63
00:05:26,840 --> 00:05:29,200
Coffee. Your Ms. Meng brought it.

64
00:05:29,280 --> 00:05:30,360
Thanks, Ms. Ye.

65
00:05:30,440 --> 00:05:31,440
- Thanks, Ms. Ye.
- Thanks.

66
00:05:31,520 --> 00:05:32,360
- Love you!
- Okay,

67
00:05:32,440 --> 00:05:33,440
I've got a meeting.

68
00:05:33,520 --> 00:05:35,000
We'll talk after.

69
00:05:35,640 --> 00:05:37,520
- Get back to work.
- Coffee's on Ms. Ye today!

70
00:05:37,600 --> 00:05:38,440
- Thanks.
- Thank you.

71
00:05:47,280 --> 00:05:48,800
Ye Meng, welcome home.

72
00:05:52,080 --> 00:05:54,120
What's wrong with you?

73
00:05:56,600 --> 00:05:58,320
Sit down.

74
00:05:58,400 --> 00:06:00,800
Look at you, back from Jiangbei, glowing.

75
00:06:01,600 --> 00:06:02,880
Must be the weather.

76
00:06:02,960 --> 00:06:03,800
Yeah, weather's nice.

77
00:06:05,800 --> 00:06:07,280
And it sounded lively outside.

78
00:06:08,960 --> 00:06:10,480
Buying coffee for the team?

79
00:06:13,880 --> 00:06:14,920
Nice.

80
00:06:20,160 --> 00:06:21,960
So, how long are you staying this time?

81
00:06:27,080 --> 00:06:27,920
For good?

82
00:06:39,720 --> 00:06:41,080
Here's that file you wanted.

83
00:06:42,320 --> 00:06:43,160
Take a look.

84
00:06:47,720 --> 00:06:49,360
You think I'd lie to you?

85
00:06:49,440 --> 00:06:51,040
WANG XINGSHENG, MALE

86
00:06:51,120 --> 00:06:53,360
AUGUST 25, 1979, BACHELOR'S DEGREE

87
00:07:04,040 --> 00:07:06,480
HEALTHY, NOT OVERSEAS CHINESE

88
00:07:09,000 --> 00:07:10,520
When can I meet him?

89
00:07:11,680 --> 00:07:13,080
What's the rush?

90
00:07:16,040 --> 00:07:17,880
If you're too busy,
just give me his contact.

91
00:07:18,480 --> 00:07:19,800
I'll meet him myself.

92
00:07:19,880 --> 00:07:21,760
I said don't rush.

93
00:07:21,840 --> 00:07:22,760
Have some water.

94
00:07:27,920 --> 00:07:31,360
The problem is…

95
00:07:32,440 --> 00:07:34,120
you're not a company employee.

96
00:07:34,200 --> 00:07:35,640
I can't just hand out client details,

97
00:07:36,360 --> 00:07:38,600
- right?
- Really?

98
00:07:58,560 --> 00:08:00,400
Don't worry, I've already arranged it.

99
00:08:00,480 --> 00:08:01,760
Tomorrow at 2 p.m.,

100
00:08:01,840 --> 00:08:02,960
I'll take you to meet him.

101
00:08:03,560 --> 00:08:05,760
- Alright?
- Thanks.

102
00:08:07,800 --> 00:08:10,560
The Three Musketeers,
finally together again.

103
00:08:10,640 --> 00:08:12,440
Come on. No more long faces.

104
00:08:12,520 --> 00:08:13,480
Let's take a photo.

105
00:08:14,400 --> 00:08:17,760
Here. Three, two, one,

106
00:08:17,840 --> 00:08:19,480
cherries!

107
00:08:21,160 --> 00:08:22,480
I'll post it on Moments.

108
00:08:24,080 --> 00:08:25,000
No plans to come back?

109
00:08:50,960 --> 00:08:53,720
Isn't that Ye Meng's old boss?

110
00:08:54,360 --> 00:08:57,080
You really let her run back to Jiangbei
and have coffee with him?

111
00:08:58,400 --> 00:08:59,720
I'm not trying to scare you,

112
00:08:59,800 --> 00:09:02,200
but you two just got married.

113
00:09:02,280 --> 00:09:04,320
And you let her walk straight back
onto her ex's turf?

114
00:09:04,400 --> 00:09:05,360
You trust her that much?

115
00:09:06,600 --> 00:09:07,640
I do.

116
00:09:08,360 --> 00:09:11,000
I'm not trying to stir things up,
but come on,

117
00:09:12,560 --> 00:09:15,120
compared to that guy?
Sure, you've got the looks

118
00:09:16,040 --> 00:09:17,280
and the charm.

119
00:09:17,960 --> 00:09:19,240
But look at that big office.

120
00:09:19,320 --> 00:09:20,760
The man's got serious money.

121
00:09:20,840 --> 00:09:22,680
On that front, you can't compete.

122
00:09:22,760 --> 00:09:25,240
And don't forget. They've got history.

123
00:09:27,280 --> 00:09:28,840
That's dangerous.

124
00:09:30,560 --> 00:09:33,360
- You're insane.
- Don't brush it off.

125
00:09:33,440 --> 00:09:34,800
I've seen this before.

126
00:09:36,840 --> 00:09:38,520
Look at Fang Ya'en.

127
00:09:38,600 --> 00:09:39,840
She said she hated her ex,

128
00:09:40,480 --> 00:09:42,680
swore she'd divorce him.
And now? Still stuck.

129
00:09:43,240 --> 00:09:45,080
You'd better be careful.

130
00:09:45,160 --> 00:09:47,680
I'm not like you.

131
00:09:47,760 --> 00:09:48,600
We've registered.

132
00:09:51,320 --> 00:09:53,040
Yeah, yeah. You've got the certificate.

133
00:09:53,120 --> 00:09:55,720
But you're here drinking with me,
while she's out with her ex.

134
00:10:02,840 --> 00:10:03,680
I've got a move.

135
00:10:04,840 --> 00:10:05,840
Guaranteed to pull

136
00:10:05,920 --> 00:10:07,840
Ye Meng's attention
back to you in no time.

137
00:10:07,920 --> 00:10:09,080
What move?

138
00:10:09,680 --> 00:10:11,640
See those two?

139
00:10:11,720 --> 00:10:13,080
Old friends of mine.

140
00:10:13,160 --> 00:10:14,200
I'll say hi,

141
00:10:14,280 --> 00:10:15,880
snap a couple of close shots.

142
00:10:15,960 --> 00:10:17,200
Fake it so it looks intimate.

143
00:10:17,280 --> 00:10:18,680
She can post, so can you.

144
00:10:18,760 --> 00:10:20,680
- Let her stew a little.
- That's childish.

145
00:10:20,760 --> 00:10:21,880
Come on. Try it.

146
00:10:21,960 --> 00:10:22,840
- Might work.
- No, thanks.

147
00:10:22,920 --> 00:10:24,120
Come on.

148
00:10:24,200 --> 00:10:26,680
- Go. I'm trying to save your marriage.
- Not happening.

149
00:10:28,040 --> 00:10:29,080
Mr. Cheng.

150
00:10:33,440 --> 00:10:34,760
Jiang Luzhi?

151
00:10:34,840 --> 00:10:35,800
What are you doing here?

152
00:10:35,880 --> 00:10:37,880
Bringing you business.

153
00:10:38,680 --> 00:10:40,680
Some new Hailan Port merchants

154
00:10:40,760 --> 00:10:42,480
need a place for team building.

155
00:10:42,560 --> 00:10:43,480
I recommended your bar.

156
00:10:43,560 --> 00:10:45,040
Appreciate it, Ms. Jiang.

157
00:10:45,120 --> 00:10:47,720
I'm always in for business.

158
00:10:47,800 --> 00:10:49,400
Funny though,

159
00:10:49,480 --> 00:10:51,400
you and Ye Meng aren't exactly friends.

160
00:10:52,000 --> 00:10:53,920
And considering you two

161
00:10:54,000 --> 00:10:55,560
shared…

162
00:10:56,920 --> 00:10:57,840
the same man…

163
00:10:59,480 --> 00:11:01,320
Since when do you
throw me a bone like this?

164
00:11:02,280 --> 00:11:04,600
And you think women are the ones
who obsess over love?

165
00:11:04,680 --> 00:11:06,040
Men are worse.

166
00:11:06,640 --> 00:11:09,360
Can't you stop being so narrow-minded?

167
00:11:09,440 --> 00:11:11,960
I recommended your place
because it's good.

168
00:11:12,040 --> 00:11:13,960
I get to build favors on both sides.

169
00:11:14,040 --> 00:11:16,040
Why cut off business
just to hold a grudge?

170
00:11:17,400 --> 00:11:19,240
Smart woman. Drink's on me.

171
00:11:19,320 --> 00:11:20,720
I drove. No alcohol.

172
00:11:20,800 --> 00:11:22,360
Then a mocktail.

173
00:11:22,440 --> 00:11:23,520
Sit, relax.

174
00:11:24,240 --> 00:11:26,120
Stop being so narrow-minded.

175
00:11:31,440 --> 00:11:33,080
How long are you planning to pretend

176
00:11:33,160 --> 00:11:34,520
we're strangers?

177
00:11:35,120 --> 00:11:36,040
We were never close.

178
00:11:39,640 --> 00:11:42,520
I thought you two were done ages ago.

179
00:11:42,600 --> 00:11:43,960
Then, the other day,

180
00:11:44,040 --> 00:11:45,840
I saw her make it official on Moments.

181
00:11:47,280 --> 00:11:50,240
Didn't expect her
to take someone so seriously.

182
00:11:51,080 --> 00:11:53,000
So, let me wish you well.

183
00:11:53,080 --> 00:11:54,920
Hope it lasts.

184
00:11:55,000 --> 00:11:56,000
And

185
00:11:56,080 --> 00:11:58,840
that you've got enough charm
to keep her here in Ningsui.

186
00:12:02,360 --> 00:12:04,120
You're that worried
she'll go back to Jiangbei?

187
00:12:04,840 --> 00:12:06,160
And you're not?

188
00:12:15,520 --> 00:12:18,080
Here, take a look at the drinks list.

189
00:12:25,320 --> 00:12:27,520
- I need to take this.
- Go ahead.

190
00:12:27,600 --> 00:12:28,840
Hi, Mom.

191
00:12:28,920 --> 00:12:30,800
I'm working late.

192
00:12:31,440 --> 00:12:34,080
Jiang Luzhi's parents are teachers,

193
00:12:34,160 --> 00:12:35,520
known for being strict.

194
00:12:35,600 --> 00:12:37,200
Her family's just like Ye Meng's.

195
00:12:37,280 --> 00:12:40,720
- They both want marriages with local boys.
- No, I am not at a bar. I…

196
00:12:40,800 --> 00:12:42,480
That's why she was set up with you.

197
00:12:42,560 --> 00:12:43,840
What's on your phone?

198
00:12:44,680 --> 00:12:46,280
This picture?

199
00:12:46,840 --> 00:12:47,680
Look at that.

200
00:12:49,160 --> 00:12:50,840
Imagine Ye seeing it,

201
00:12:50,920 --> 00:12:51,960
with Jiang Luzhi in the shot.

202
00:12:52,040 --> 00:12:53,760
Double the effect, right?

203
00:12:53,840 --> 00:12:55,040
Look how close you two are.

204
00:12:56,000 --> 00:12:58,000
More like double the disaster. Delete it.

205
00:12:59,560 --> 00:13:00,400
Sent.

206
00:13:00,480 --> 00:13:01,760
You had to touch my phone.

207
00:13:01,840 --> 00:13:03,920
Look what you did, making such a…

208
00:13:04,640 --> 00:13:06,320
huge deal out of it.

209
00:13:08,160 --> 00:13:10,680
Ye Meng will be back any minute.
You're welcome.

210
00:13:12,120 --> 00:13:13,080
Rest assured.

211
00:13:20,080 --> 00:13:22,440
Look at your faces. Priceless.

212
00:13:23,760 --> 00:13:27,320
Check it out. So many likes.
Everyone's hoping you'll come back.

213
00:13:31,240 --> 00:13:32,880
It's not just me.

214
00:13:32,960 --> 00:13:33,880
Even Tai Mingxiao

215
00:13:33,960 --> 00:13:35,960
keeps saying new clients are impossible.

216
00:13:36,680 --> 00:13:38,600
Without you, PR's a mess.

217
00:13:38,680 --> 00:13:40,720
And projects are piling up this year.

218
00:13:42,560 --> 00:13:45,000
Didn't you once say you wanted
to buy a place in Jiangbei?

219
00:13:45,080 --> 00:13:47,480
This could be the perfect chance.

220
00:13:47,560 --> 00:13:48,720
Think about it.

221
00:13:49,560 --> 00:13:52,160
I'm happy the company's doing well.

222
00:13:52,240 --> 00:13:53,440
But I'm fine where I am.

223
00:13:53,520 --> 00:13:56,320
I like the pace of life back home.

224
00:13:56,400 --> 00:13:57,240
Anyway, I should go.

225
00:13:57,320 --> 00:13:58,280
Hold on.

226
00:13:59,520 --> 00:14:01,600
After everything I've done for you,

227
00:14:01,680 --> 00:14:02,520
how about dinner?

228
00:14:02,600 --> 00:14:05,160
Not tonight. I'm really not in the mood.

229
00:14:05,240 --> 00:14:06,120
Another time.

230
00:14:08,840 --> 00:14:10,320
Is this about Wang Xingsheng?

231
00:14:11,280 --> 00:14:12,840
Or that so-called boyfriend of yours?

232
00:14:13,360 --> 00:14:14,600
Come on. Just let him know.

233
00:14:14,680 --> 00:14:15,800
He won't mind.

234
00:14:16,440 --> 00:14:17,640
He's a grown man, isn't he?

235
00:14:19,040 --> 00:14:20,480
Sorry.

236
00:14:20,560 --> 00:14:22,240
I don't want to risk making him jealous.

237
00:14:22,320 --> 00:14:23,720
And he's not my boyfriend.

238
00:14:23,800 --> 00:14:24,880
He's my husband.

239
00:14:25,560 --> 00:14:27,120
We've already registered.

240
00:14:27,200 --> 00:14:28,720
When we hold the wedding,

241
00:14:28,800 --> 00:14:30,560
you'll get an invitation.
Now, I'm leaving.

242
00:14:32,200 --> 00:14:33,520
- Bye.
- Bye.

243
00:14:34,440 --> 00:14:36,680
Bye? What the hell just happened?

244
00:14:39,000 --> 00:14:40,600
It's real.

245
00:14:40,680 --> 00:14:42,760
I double-checked. Genuine.

246
00:14:42,840 --> 00:14:44,200
You double-checked?

247
00:14:56,280 --> 00:14:57,840
Oh no, no, no.

248
00:14:57,920 --> 00:14:59,280
<i>This is suicide.</i>

249
00:14:59,360 --> 00:15:01,280
<i>Delete it before it explodes.</i>

250
00:15:01,360 --> 00:15:02,520
<i>Got a death wish?</i>

251
00:15:02,600 --> 00:15:04,360
CHENG KAIRAN'S POST
OLD FRIENDS CATCHING UP OVER BUSINESS

252
00:15:04,440 --> 00:15:07,000
I'll head out. Taking this with me.

253
00:15:10,960 --> 00:15:12,400
<i>Drinking's bad for your health.</i>

254
00:15:12,480 --> 00:15:14,440
<i>Keep it in moderation.</i>

255
00:15:14,520 --> 00:15:16,080
<i>PS. Jinyu looks good.</i>

256
00:15:16,160 --> 00:15:20,240
JIAYU'S COMMENT

257
00:15:20,320 --> 00:15:21,240
CHENG KAIRAN REPLIED

258
00:15:21,320 --> 00:15:22,680
<i>Sorry, forgot to set the groups.</i>

259
00:15:24,440 --> 00:15:25,640
Kai,

260
00:15:25,720 --> 00:15:26,960
you trying to get yourself killed?

261
00:15:27,840 --> 00:15:29,760
Killed? Please.

262
00:15:29,840 --> 00:15:31,360
This is what we call a love test.

263
00:15:31,440 --> 00:15:33,400
If a woman really loves you,

264
00:15:33,480 --> 00:15:36,120
the second another girl
comes within 16 feet,

265
00:15:36,200 --> 00:15:38,080
she'll tense up.

266
00:15:38,160 --> 00:15:40,080
If that girl happens to be your type,

267
00:15:40,160 --> 00:15:41,400
she'll zoom in with a sniper scope

268
00:15:41,480 --> 00:15:42,680
and take her out instantly.

269
00:15:42,760 --> 00:15:44,800
Oh, so now you're an expert?

270
00:15:45,520 --> 00:15:46,480
Of course.

271
00:15:47,480 --> 00:15:49,600
Jealousy turns women superhuman
on the spot,

272
