00:30:09,120 --> 00:30:10,680
I need to ask you something.

538
00:30:18,040 --> 00:30:19,000
<i>Wang Xingsheng's hotel.</i>

539
00:30:19,080 --> 00:30:21,840
<i>Got it out of Gou Kai's driver.</i>

540
00:30:23,480 --> 00:30:25,080
Thanks. Dinner's on me next time.

541
00:30:30,640 --> 00:30:32,120
Take it easy, Grandma.

542
00:30:32,200 --> 00:30:33,560
Here, let me record you.

543
00:30:36,760 --> 00:30:37,960
Grandma,

544
00:30:38,040 --> 00:30:39,960
now that you've got
a granddaughter-in-law on the way,

545
00:30:40,040 --> 00:30:41,200
you've got extra energy, huh?

546
00:30:41,280 --> 00:30:44,880
Of course. A happy heart
keeps the body moving!

547
00:30:48,480 --> 00:30:51,240
Jinyu, you've been staring
at that same page forever.

548
00:30:51,320 --> 00:30:52,440
You zoned out.

549
00:30:53,160 --> 00:30:54,160
You don't know it.

550
00:30:54,240 --> 00:30:56,440
This is called the memory palace method.

551
00:30:57,720 --> 00:30:59,560
Memory palace, my foot.

552
00:30:59,640 --> 00:31:00,600
You just miss Ye Meng.

553
00:31:05,560 --> 00:31:06,680
I've already decided.

554
00:31:06,760 --> 00:31:07,880
When Badou gets married,

555
00:31:07,960 --> 00:31:09,280
I'm wearing red high heels.

556
00:31:09,360 --> 00:31:10,560
Okay, Grandma, sit down and rest.

557
00:31:10,640 --> 00:31:11,960
I'll get you some water.

558
00:31:36,200 --> 00:31:37,320
- Hello.
- Hi.

559
00:31:37,400 --> 00:31:39,720
I'm looking for a guest
named Wang Xingsheng.

560
00:31:39,800 --> 00:31:40,880
I'm sorry, we can't share

561
00:31:40,960 --> 00:31:42,600
- guest information.
- Please,

562
00:31:42,680 --> 00:31:44,120
I was supposed to meet him at two.

563
00:31:44,200 --> 00:31:45,920
I can't get him on the phone.

564
00:31:46,000 --> 00:31:47,920
He has a heart condition. I'm worried.

565
00:31:48,000 --> 00:31:49,600
Do you know his room number?

566
00:31:49,680 --> 00:31:51,360
I don't.

567
00:31:51,440 --> 00:31:53,560
- I just need you to help me reach him.
- One moment.

568
00:31:55,040 --> 00:31:56,600
Could you confirm the name again?

569
00:31:56,680 --> 00:31:57,520
Wang Xingsheng.

570
00:31:57,600 --> 00:32:00,440
Xing as in "prosper", Sheng as in "life".

571
00:32:01,560 --> 00:32:02,640
I'm sorry.

572
00:32:02,720 --> 00:32:04,560
Your friend checked out this morning.

573
00:32:05,680 --> 00:32:07,040
He checked out?

574
00:32:08,200 --> 00:32:09,560
Maybe try calling again?

575
00:32:12,160 --> 00:32:13,920
- Thank you.
- You're welcome.

576
00:32:44,120 --> 00:32:45,800
<i>You had him leave, didn't you?</i>

577
00:32:45,880 --> 00:32:47,400
It's one thing not to help me,

578
00:32:47,480 --> 00:32:49,520
but sabotaging me?
Isn't that going too far?

579
00:32:50,840 --> 00:32:52,240
I did cancel the meeting.

580
00:32:52,840 --> 00:32:54,520
But weren't you the one who said

581
00:32:54,600 --> 00:32:56,160
you'd track him down yourself?

582
00:32:59,200 --> 00:33:00,440
Ye Meng,

583
00:33:00,520 --> 00:33:02,520
it's not too late to change your mind.

584
00:33:02,600 --> 00:33:04,320
I'll help you find Wang Xingsheng.

585
00:33:04,920 --> 00:33:06,520
But my terms haven't changed.

586
00:34:23,199 --> 00:34:24,320
VIDEO CALL

587
00:34:24,400 --> 00:34:26,440
AWAITING RESPONSE

588
00:34:32,040 --> 00:34:32,880
<i>Hello?</i>

589
00:34:34,600 --> 00:34:36,280
I'm in a terrible mood.

590
00:34:37,159 --> 00:34:38,639
Can you cheer me up?

591
00:34:39,520 --> 00:34:41,120
<i>I don't really feel like it.</i>

592
00:34:43,400 --> 00:34:44,480
What do you mean?

593
00:34:45,480 --> 00:34:46,520
<i>Nothing.</i>

594
00:34:49,000 --> 00:34:50,360
Li Jinyu, what now?

595
00:34:50,440 --> 00:34:52,199
Ready to trade me in for a new wife?

596
00:34:52,280 --> 00:34:53,760
Why won't you comfort me?

597
00:34:59,800 --> 00:35:01,520
In about two seconds,
I'm going to hold my wife.

598
00:35:01,600 --> 00:35:03,720
So, I don't have time
to comfort her over the phone.

599
00:35:42,840 --> 00:35:44,440
What are you doing?

600
00:36:33,960 --> 00:36:35,160
Why did you come here?

601
00:36:35,800 --> 00:36:37,400
I missed you so much, I was going crazy.

602
00:36:40,800 --> 00:36:42,920
There's something I need to explain first.

603
00:36:44,120 --> 00:36:45,120
What is it?

604
00:36:47,360 --> 00:36:49,680
I'll tell you, but…

605
00:36:49,760 --> 00:36:51,200
promise me you won't get mad.

606
00:36:52,200 --> 00:36:53,720
And promise you won't get jealous.

607
00:36:53,800 --> 00:36:55,520
I can probably manage not to get mad.

608
00:36:55,600 --> 00:36:57,840
But not jealous?
I'll have to think about that one.

609
00:36:59,480 --> 00:37:01,920
After our video call last night,

610
00:37:02,000 --> 00:37:03,200
Gou Kai came over.

611
00:37:04,440 --> 00:37:05,920
I know.

612
00:37:06,000 --> 00:37:07,680
The call never disconnected.

613
00:37:07,760 --> 00:37:08,920
I heard every word.

614
00:37:09,840 --> 00:37:11,600
Then you know I kicked him out, right?

615
00:37:12,240 --> 00:37:13,600
Do you regret it?

616
00:37:14,240 --> 00:37:15,840
He wasn't wrong about one thing.

617
00:37:15,920 --> 00:37:17,400
I don't have much to give you.

618
00:37:19,280 --> 00:37:20,480
What you give me…

619
00:37:21,320 --> 00:37:22,400
no one else can.

620
00:37:23,840 --> 00:37:24,800
Like what exactly?

621
00:37:27,480 --> 00:37:29,240
Like the way you just said,

622
00:37:30,240 --> 00:37:31,920
"I missed you so much, I was going crazy."

623
00:37:32,720 --> 00:37:33,920
That's incredibly sexy.

624
00:37:34,720 --> 00:37:36,520
Sexier than me playing the guitar?

625
00:37:37,960 --> 00:37:40,280
Playing is still number one.
That line comes in third.

626
00:37:41,960 --> 00:37:42,800
What's second?

627
00:37:44,920 --> 00:37:46,960
Second was on our wedding night,

628
00:37:47,560 --> 00:37:49,240
when you called me honey.

629
00:37:52,600 --> 00:37:54,560
Actually, why don't you
put the two together?

630
00:37:55,360 --> 00:37:56,840
That might move it up to number one.

631
00:37:59,920 --> 00:38:00,960
Honey…

632
00:38:01,840 --> 00:38:03,520
I missed you so much, I was going crazy.

633
00:38:18,080 --> 00:38:20,400
GOU KAI

634
00:38:25,520 --> 00:38:26,360
What is it?

635
00:38:26,960 --> 00:38:27,840
<i>Still at the hotel?</i>

636
00:38:27,920 --> 00:38:30,160
- <i>I'm coming by.</i>
- Don't bother.

637
00:38:30,240 --> 00:38:31,320
I don't want to see you.

638
00:38:32,760 --> 00:38:34,120
<i>Don't take it the wrong way.</i>

639
00:38:34,720 --> 00:38:36,280
<i>I just want to apologize.</i>

640
00:38:36,880 --> 00:38:38,160
Had a few drinks last night,

641
00:38:38,240 --> 00:38:40,480
talked nonsense. Forget it.

642
00:38:41,160 --> 00:38:42,720
I'll keep helping you with Wang Xingsheng.

643
00:38:44,600 --> 00:38:45,480
That won't be necessary.

644
00:38:46,080 --> 00:38:48,840
My husband came to see me.
He'll help me find him.

645
00:38:48,920 --> 00:38:50,280
<i>Her husband's here?</i>

646
00:38:56,080 --> 00:38:57,920
Tell her to bring him along.

647
00:38:58,000 --> 00:39:00,440
We'll have dinner at the usual spot.

648
00:39:00,520 --> 00:39:02,600
We're busy. I'm hanging up.

649
00:39:04,360 --> 00:39:07,160
You three… even have a usual spot?

650
00:39:08,480 --> 00:39:10,840
Didn't I make myself clear just now?

651
00:39:10,920 --> 00:39:13,760
I don't tolerate anyone
trying to interfere in my marriage.

652
00:39:13,840 --> 00:39:14,840
I swear it.

653
00:39:19,080 --> 00:39:21,520
- Where are you going?
- Taking a shower.

654
00:39:30,680 --> 00:39:31,520
She hung up.

655
00:39:33,320 --> 00:39:34,600
Here's my advice.

656
00:39:34,680 --> 00:39:36,760
You need to face the truth.

657
00:39:36,840 --> 00:39:38,240
You didn't believe she was married.

658
00:39:38,320 --> 00:39:40,440
But now her husband's
right there with her.

659
00:39:41,320 --> 00:39:43,120
It's not like

660
00:39:43,200 --> 00:39:45,000
she hired an actor, right?

661
00:39:51,680 --> 00:39:53,080
Don't rule it out.

662
00:39:55,200 --> 00:39:57,520
Think about it.
Neither of us has actually seen him.

663
00:39:58,120 --> 00:39:59,120
Have you seen him?

664
00:40:02,080 --> 00:40:03,280
Exactly. I haven't either.

665
00:40:03,920 --> 00:40:05,080
So, maybe it's all an act.

666
00:40:08,280 --> 00:40:10,240
I've got to hand it to you.

667
00:40:10,320 --> 00:40:12,600
I'm seriously impressed. Respect.

668
00:40:13,680 --> 00:40:15,040
I didn't think

669
00:40:15,120 --> 00:40:18,760
you liked Ye Meng that much.
You go to Ningsui once and come back

670
00:40:18,840 --> 00:40:19,760
head over heels?

671
00:40:21,000 --> 00:40:22,880
I can admit defeat
to someone better than me.

672
00:40:22,960 --> 00:40:24,800
But what decent guy
could she find in Ningsui?

673
00:40:24,880 --> 00:40:26,040
I can't accept it.

674
00:40:27,760 --> 00:40:28,680
All an act.

675
00:40:35,480 --> 00:40:36,880
CHENG KAIRAN

676
00:40:42,640 --> 00:40:43,480
Yeah?

677
00:40:44,240 --> 00:40:45,360
<i>I dug something up on him.</i>

678
00:40:46,280 --> 00:40:47,120
Go on.

679
00:40:47,800 --> 00:40:49,280
<i>Fat Buddha's back in Jiangbei.</i>

680
00:40:57,240 --> 00:40:58,800
You're sure?

681
00:40:58,880 --> 00:41:00,360
<i>Positive. Chen told me.</i>

682
00:41:00,440 --> 00:41:02,920
<i>Turns out the guy was just</i>
<i>peddling fake antiques.</i>

683
00:41:03,000 --> 00:41:04,840
<i>Never handled the real deal.</i>

684
00:41:04,920 --> 00:41:06,760
<i>He just got out after being locked up</i>

685
00:41:06,840 --> 00:41:07,840
<i>for driving a fake-plate car</i>

686
00:41:07,920 --> 00:41:09,640
<i>and getting into a gang fight.</i>

687
00:41:09,720 --> 00:41:12,200
<i>Oh, and he runs a teahouse in Jiangbei.</i>

688
00:41:12,280 --> 00:41:13,720
<i>I've sent you the address.</i>

689
00:41:14,480 --> 00:41:15,440
Got it. Thanks.

690
00:41:18,680 --> 00:41:20,040
So, you both decided to step in?

691
00:41:21,440 --> 00:41:22,840
I asked him for a favor.

692
00:41:23,760 --> 00:41:25,200
Can we really count on Fat Buddha?

693
00:41:25,280 --> 00:41:27,040
We basically put him in jail not long ago.

694
00:41:28,000 --> 00:41:30,560
Doesn't matter.
We'll never know if we don't try.

695
